entropy.solver

Class NonViableSourceConfigurationException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • entropy.solver.PlanException
          • entropy.solver.NonViableSourceConfigurationException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class NonViableSourceConfigurationException
extends PlanException
    An exception to describe a non viable source configuration for a planning problem. A configuration is not viable if for one node, the sum of CPU consumptions or memory consumptions is superior to the CPU or the memory capacity of the node.
    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
